name: Cat Walk (Zac E)
description:
Cat Walk is a cat fashion game. 

Wear the right clothes to themed parties and get insider info on what clothing styles each company likes.  It's not all sunshine and rainbows, you've got to earn enough FishCoins to pay your debt at the end of each week.  

This project the made for the Extra Credits Game Jam #3, with the theme of cycles.

Tips:
You have two equip slots (Head, Body)

Controls:
You play with the mouse only.
